source.name: 2009-2011 American Community Survey 3-Year Estimates Summary File
source.description: A nationwide survey that collects information such as age, race, income, commute time to work, home value, veteran status, and other data. Data from the American Community Survey and the Puerto Rico Community Survey were collected during calendar years 2009 through 2011. Available for geographic areas with populations of 20,000 or more.
